{
  "stem": "13874.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had each a traditional system which would take care of all the criminals, whatever is there, and then, of course, illegal things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And here comes the concentration camps, where outside their jurisdiction they could do what they pleased.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And if they didn't like what you said, you got there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, it's a big difference between the Jews and the others, where the Jews were released.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was released under the conditions that I leave Germany in six months.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when-- once I was out there, I could tell as much as I wanted about if they listened.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and the rest of the world, including the United States, they say, oh, it's only Jews-- who cares?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was the impressions they could find.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "However, the Germans in the concentration camp, when any family member was put in the concentration camp, the family had to be super Nazis.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had to be very careful not to talk to anybody who might be politically not correct.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Their children couldn't talk about their parents, and they could not be seen next to a Jewish kid in the school or anything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think there was one fellow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know there was one fellow in the-- in class.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "His father was sent to Dachau-- to concentration-- but he was away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He-- I don't know what was-- he was away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was particularly careful to stay away from me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He wouldn't come to me in sympathy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- so-- all the-- and there were strict censorship of mail, of telephones, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Germans, if you had a family member in the concentration camp, they could not write abroad about that somebody was there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was strictly forbidden.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
